Interface FoundPointSO

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DetectDescribePoint<T,Desc>, InterestPointDetector<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DetectDescribe_CompleteSift, DetectDescribeFusion, GeneralToInterestPoint, InterestPointDetectorOverride, SurfPlanar_to_DetectDescribePoint, WrapDetectDescribeSurf, WrapFHtoInterestPoint, WrapFLPtoInterestPoint, WrapFPtoInterestPoint, WrapSiftDetector

    public interface FoundPointSO
    List of detected features that are invariant to scale and in-plane rotation. PointSO is short for Point Scale-Orientation.
